A little girl went to a pet shop and asked,
"Excuse me, excuse me, do you have any rabbits?"
"If you go down this aisle we have black rabbits."
"And if you go down this aisle we have white rabbits."
"And if you go down this aisle we have brown rabbits."
"What kind of rabbit would you like?"
"Well, I don't think my pet snake really cares."
